val linesDStream = KafkaUtils.createDirectStream[String, String](ssc, kafkaParams, topicsSet)
 linesDStream.print
 val valuesDStream = linesDStream.map(_._2)

    valuesDStream.foreachRDD { rdd =>
      // There exists at least one element in RDD
      if (!rdd.isEmpty) {
        val count = rdd.count
        println("count received " + count)
        import sqlContext.implicits._
        import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._
        val df = sqlContext.read.schema(schema).json(rdd)
        df.show
        df.registerTempTable("uber")

        val countsDF = df.groupBy($"cluster", hour($"dt")).count()
        countsDF.registerTempTable("uber_counts")
        
      }
    }
ssc.remember(Minutes(1)) 

ssc.start() 
ssc.awaitTerminationOrTimeout(1 * 5 * 1000)
%sql  select cluster, count(cluster) as count from uber group by cluster
%sql SELECT hour(uber.dt) as hr,count(cluster) as ct FROM uber group By hour(uber.dt)
%sql SELECT hour(uber.dt) as hr, cluster, count(cluster) as ct FROM uber group By hour(uber.dt), cluster

%sql
SELECT cluster,dayofmonth(uber.dt) as day , hour(uber.dt) as hour, count(cluster) as ct  FROM uber  GROUP BY cluster,dayofmonth(uber.dt), hour(uber.dt)
%sql select cluster, sum(count) as total_count from uber_counts group by cluster
%sql select cluster,  dt, count(cluster) as count from uber group by dt, cluster  order by dt, cluster
